OL,3,CMass inspections announced amid
OL,4,Cfuneral directors probe
OL,6,FEvery funeral director in Hull and
OL,7,FEast Yorkshire will be inspected after
OL,8,Fpolice launched an investigation into
OL,9,Falleged malpractice at one business.
OL,11,FHull City Council and East Riding
OL,12,FCouncil have written to funeral
OL,13,Fdirectors informing them of the
OL,14,Fvisits, which are supported by
OL,15,Findustry bodies.
OL,17,FJulia Weldon, Hull's director of
OL,18,Fpublic health, said the move would
OL,19,Fhelp to reassure people in the wake of
OL,20,Fthe investigation into Legacy
OL,21,FIndependent Funeral Directors.
