OL,6,FShe said: "We know that bereaved
OL,7,Ffamilies will have seen the recent
OL,8,Freports and will be seeking
OL,9,Freassurance at what is already a very
OL,10,Fdifficult time. These visits are a
OL,11,Fchance for both local authorities to
OL,12,Fwork with our local businesses to put
OL,13,Fthose reassurances in place."
OL,15,FHumberside Police started
OL,16,Finvestigating Legacy after concerns
OL,17,Fwere raised on 6 March about the care
OL,18,Fof bodies.
