OL,6,FThe visits have the support of the
OL,7,FNational Association of Funeral
OL,8,FDirectors and the National Society of
OL,9,FAllied and Independent Funeral
OL,10,FDirectors.
OL,12,FAndy Kingdom, public health director
OL,13,Ffor East Riding Council, said: "While
OL,14,Four main focus at the moment is on
OL,15,Fsupporting the families directly
OL,16,Faffected by this very upsetting
OL,17,Fsituation, it is also important that
OL,18,Fwe work together to ensure confidence,
OL,19,Ftrust and the high standards people
OL,20,Fmust be able to expect from the
OL,21,Fsector."
