OL,6,FThe investigation into Legacy has
OL,7,Fprompted .
OL,9,FMark Horton, president of the National
OL,10,FSociety of Allied and Independent
OL,11,FFuneral Directors (SAIF), wants
OL,12,Fstatutory regulation.
OL,14,FHe said: "We want to reassure families
OL,15,Fthat all our members adhere to strict
OL,16,Fregulation and standards. All are
OL,17,Fprofessional funeral directors. I
OL,18,Fwelcome regulation across the UK, so
OL,19,Ffamilies can be reassured their loved
OL,20,Fones are looked after in a dignified
OL,21,Fway."
